item.title: Add Our Calendar
item.description: To add the UMFC calendar to Google Calendar: Visit Google Calendar. Click on the arrow next to “Other Calendars.” Select “Add a friend’s calendar.” Paste in umich.edu_toeb19ptci3123vprh6464i308@group.calendar.google.com Click “Add.”

item.title: Schedule
item.description: This calendar is regularly updated with practice times, competitions, and other events. Add it to your calendar to stay updated.
